            <title>[PDFBOX-5798] Observable Timing Discrepancy (Timing Attack)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5798</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A static analyse tool is reporting:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An attacker can guess the secret value of digest because it is compared using java.util.Arrays.equals, which is vulnerable to timing attacks. Use java.security.MessageDigest.isEqual to compare values securely.&lt;br/&gt;
&#8206;pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdmodel/encryption/StandardSecurityHandler.java&lt;/p&gt;</description>
